episodes.title: Autism VS Cults... Where's the common ground?
episodes.description:
A somewhat scattered look at commonalities of traits and struggles of people who were late-diagnosed autistic and those who were raised by cults and escaped as adults... Do you see the similarities that I see? Is it just me? Have you ever related to a group of people you have nothing in common with? 

Let's chat about it.
